<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">5月28日，我校一届四次教职工暨工会会员代表大会在学术报告厅胜利召开。校党委书记、督导专员江延湖出席并讲话，校党委副书记、执行校长范红铭、全体在家校领导和200余名教代会正式代表、特邀代表和列席代表参加。校纪委书记、副校长张永革主持。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-05-30%2013%3A01%3A59%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%871.png?Expires=2032405319&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=l9gwnwouNdF1XiZldyq28MMKVpo%3D" alt="" width="650" height="365" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">大会上，江延湖指出，本次大会是在全校上下深入学习贯彻习近平新时代中国特色社会主义思想和习近平总书记考察江西重要讲话精神，加快推进学校高质量发展，喜迎先锋集团创建30周年和江西软件大学建校20周年的关键时期召开的一次重要会议。他强调，要把抓机遇、抓落实作为一切工作的生命线，锚定学校发展的目标，敢作敢为，善作善成，推进学校高质量发展。一是要抢抓机遇、乘势而上，把奋进步伐迈得更好，二是以校庆为契机，加快提升办学质量，三是敢于担当、攻坚克难，将工作本领提升得更高，四是以生为本、以师为尊，让发展之路走得更稳。以“大抓落实年”的实绩实效，共同推进学校各项事业健康快速发展。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-05-30%2013%3A06%3A30%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%872.png?Expires=2032405590&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=1%2F%2Bgw7rSQspaLYRQ%2FDnCqkOJs%2Fs%3D" alt="" width="650" height="365" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">范红铭在学校工作报告中客观总结、系统梳理了学校过去一年来在教育教学、科研创新、学生管理等方面取得的主要成绩，在2023年度江西省民办高校年检和综合考核中，我校跃居全省同类本科院校第4位，充分展示了学校内涵发展、特色发展、创新发展的丰硕成果，深入分析了当前面临的机遇和挑战，明确了2024年学校的重点任务。他指出，全校上下要围绕中心工作，以持续推进“强化内涵、突出特色、创建标杆、促进提升”为主线，以年检和综合考核为契机，以“本科层次职业学校本科教学工作合格评估指标和基本要求”为导向，在建设有特色、有品质、有情怀、有作为的高水平职业技术大学的道路上迈出更加坚实步伐，以新的更大的成绩向20周年校庆献礼。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-05-30%2013%3A07%3A42%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%873.png?Expires=2032405663&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=poYbIFHfhUXDn4gI3OE1j0baLjI%3D" alt="" width="650" height="433" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">本次大会听取审议并通过了校党委副书记、执行校长范红铭作的《奋发图强，努力建设有特色、有品质、有情怀、有作为的高水平职业技术大学》的学校工作报告，监事会监事长汤胜红作的《监事会工作报告》，财务处处长万笠作的</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">《学校财务工作报告》；书面审议通过了工会工作报告、一届三次教代会提案办理情况报告；表决通过了增补第一届工会委员会委员的决议，通过了《江西软件职业技术大学一届四次“双代会”会议决议》</span></p><p style="text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-05-30%2013%3A09%3A12%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%874.png?Expires=2032405758&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=cT3JpbXo5hU9MA64en36kSVEwSM%3D" alt="" width="650" height="365" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">大会号召，全体教职员工要在学校党委和行政的坚强领导下，坚定不移讲政治，全力以赴谋发展，聚焦“走在前、勇争先、善作为”的目标要求，解放思想，开拓创新，扬长补短，固本兴新，为建设有特色、有品质、有情怀、有作为的高水平职业技术大学而努力奋进！</span></p><div class="foot_background_color" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 30px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-color: rgb(135, 40, 170); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap;"></div><p><br/></p>